```

---

# Express

```json
"express": "^4.15.4"
```

Web application framework.

Provides:

```text
REST APIs
Routing
Middleware
HTTP Server
```

Example:

```javascript
app.get('/products')
```

---

# MongoDB Driver

```json
"mongodb": "^4.7.0"
```

Allows application to connect to MongoDB.

Example:

```javascript
